{"tid":1384744,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"幹你娘塞爆","createTime":"2019-07-30T02:48:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T02:53:02.000Z","uid":15009,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"69357988190fd511be9a4ae0dbff56b007110c67","tid":1384744,"uid":15009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T02:48:01.000Z","msg":"我之前是在香港打工的，而我上班的原則是：<br />\n「幹你娘塞爆」<br />\n沒錯，就是幹你娘塞爆，老子才不管甚麼公司遲到三小時的，每次坐車就是姬芭的遲到。坐車變成塞車，塞車變成撞車。整個香港的上班族全都是這樣。<br />\n<br />\n我還記得，我那個月上班25天，經理跑來跟我說，這個月遲到二十六天，你有頭緒嗎？<br />\n<br />\n我他媽的怎麼會知道。"},{"pid":"17d7bc958517a9b1991050ef5b41754b55f33f9f","tid":1384744,"uid":110851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T02:53:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span><br />\n唔睇都埋嚟推下po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n[集思廣益]香城online小地圖app<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1383244\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1383244</a>"}]}